                    [Local Mac: sshpass + curl]
                         │
                    [Say MCP / say command]
\stopverb}

\p{\strong{Risk}: WiFi is the only network path. All ethernet ports show NO-CARRIER. \strong{Mitigation}: USB mics and local capture/transcription continue even if WiFi drops — data accumulates locally and can be retrieved when connectivity returns.}
}
